        "q_2_1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I know how many chews to give my dog?",
            "content": "<p>Dosing is based on your dog's weight. You'll find the complete dosing guide on each product page.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q_2_2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When is the best time to give the chews?",
            "content": "<p>Any time works. Most pet parents find it easiest to build it into an existing routine - morning feeding, an evening walk, or bedtime. If your dog's daily dose is more than one chew, consider splitting it between morning and evening. Consistency matters more than timing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q_2_3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long until I see results?",
            "content": "<p>Every dog is different, so experiences may vary. We recommend giving any supplement at least 4 to 6 weeks of consistent daily use to allow the ingredients to build up in your dog's system. As with any supplement, individual results will vary.</p>"
          }
        },
        "q_2_4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I give more than the recommended dose?",
            "content": "<p>We recommend sticking to the guidelines on the label. More is not always better with supplements - the doses are carefully calibrated to be effective at the recommended serving size.</p>"
          }
        },
